description:
This is a dataset of Illumina RNA sequencing reads, for a project investigating resistance to Pirimiphos-methyl in the major malaria vectors, Anopheles gambiae and Anopheles coluzzii. There are four biological replicates for the following conditions: 
 &nbsp; 
 Ngousso (susceptible) 
 Kisumu (susceptible) 
 Bouake gambiae unexposed 
 Bouake gambiae PM survivors 
 Bouake coluzzii unexposed&nbsp; 
 Bouake coluzzii PM&nbsp; survivors&nbsp; 
 &nbsp; 
 SRA submission: SUB14596876 
 &nbsp;

